<dl id="n26197b"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n26" href="#n26197b">N26 (VI.B.18)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n26all.htm#n26197b"> 197(b)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> Imhotep </blockquote> <dd class="well"><mm class="note">Note: Imhopt was an architect and a learned scribe of the III<sup>rd</sup> dynasty. He built the great step-pyramid of Sakkara for the king, Zoser. In Ptolemaic times Imhopt was deified. </mm> </dd></dl>
